      <li parentName="ul"><strong parentName="li"><inlineCode parentName="strong">{`--value`}</inlineCode></strong>{` The numerical value for the file size, in a unit defined by`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul"><strong parentName="li"><inlineCode parentName="strong">{`--unit`}</inlineCode></strong>{` A string to define the unit used, either `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`B`}</inlineCode>{` for bytes, `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`GB`}</inlineCode>{` for gibibytes, `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`KB`}</inlineCode>{` for kibibytes, `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`MB`}</inlineCode>{` for mebibytes, `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`PB`}</inlineCode>{` for pebibytes, or `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`TB`}</inlineCode>{` for tebibytes.`}</li>
